Package: mathgenscrape
Title: Scrape the Mathematics Genealogy Project
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Ben", "Bolker", email = "bbolker@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for querying the Mathematics Genealogy Project
    (<https://genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/>) by name or by advanced
    search fields, and for recursively tracing a mathematician's advisor
    (ancestor) or student (descendant) tree into an edge list suitable
    for graph analysis (e.g. with 'igraph').
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Imports:
    httr,
    rvest
Suggests:
    igraph,
    visNetwork
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
